    "     (standard deviation)^2 = variance\n",
    "     \n",
    "pdf(x, mean, sd) = (1 / (sqrt(2 * PI) * sd)) * exp(-((x-mean)^2)/(2*sd^2)))\n",
    "pdf(x, mean, sd) = (1 / (sqrt(2 * PI * varaince)) * exp(-((x-mean)^2)/(2*varaince)))\n",
